To activate mozc on emacs, you will need to add the following lines to
your .emacs or ${EMACS_LISPPREFIX}/site-start.el:

	(set-language-environment "Japanese")
	(require 'mozc)
	(setq default-input-method "japanese-mozc")

===========================================================================
